08/12/25: Debugging in shellscripting
======================================

 Process of finding and fixing the problem in the scripts 
 
 Procedure:
 ----------
  understand the error message
  findout what is the problem with the script
  find the error location in the scrit
  locate the line number from error message
  fix the problem
  
  debugging mode:
  ---------------
  1. disabling the shell --> -n option 
    -j ->noexecution useful to check only for syntax errors
	
   2. displaying commands while 
   
 bash -n project.sh  #-n -enable can check only syntax. can find the error in the file but not exactly where
 bash -x project.sh  #-x -enable expansion, can find with each and every lines 
 bash -v project.sh  #
 bash -nv project.sh 
 bash +xv project.sh #+xv -disable debug 
 
 type trap   #advanced topic 
  kill -l
  top 
  lsns 
  trap -l 
  man stty - need to study
  
  ps 
  ps -ef | grep java 
  kill 
  
  
09/12/2025: Introduction to SED/AWK Editor
==========================================

 SED - noninteractive stream editor # non destructive editor  
 
 sudo yum install sed -y 
 sed --version 
 syntax:
  sed '/USA/p' country.txt 
  sed -n '/USA/p' country.txt 
  
  sed '3,$d' country.txt
  sed '/Japan/d' country.txt 
  sed 's/cashew/Almond/'
  

  nano awk_emp.txt
  awk '{print $1}' awk_emp.txt 
  awk '{print $2}' emp.txt 
  aws '$2> 22000 {print $1,$2}' awk_emp.txt 
  
   
